Quote: <i>chocolate wheel</i>: At school fairs and other charity gatherings, the chocolate wheel is a traditional fundraiser. This is a WHEEL OF FORTUNE with a box of chocolates for the person who has purchased the ticket marked with the winning number. Occasionally other prizes are offered (e.g. chickens) but chocolates are the staple.
